  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p786121/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t</p>\n<p>\n\tAfter the mass shooting at a gay club in Orlando, Florida, many people are wondering: Why haven't we done more to prevent this kind of horrific tragedy?继弗罗里达<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p785569/\" target=\"_blank\">奥兰多同性俱乐部大规模枪击事件</a>后，许多人在想：为防止这类可怖的悲剧事件，我们做的还不够多吗？</p>\n<p>\n\tThis is a question and routine many Americans are accustomed to by now.这是很多美国人已经习以为常要面对的一个日常问题。</p>\n<p>\n\tFollowing a mass shooting, President Barack Obama yet again takes to the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/lectern\" target=\"_blank\">lectern</a> to address the nation on yet another horrific act of gun violence in the US, typically making no effort to hide his anger and <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/frustration\" target=\"_blank\">frustration</a>.大规模枪击之后，奥巴马又一次向全国就枪支暴力的恐怖行为走上讲坛发表演说，依旧毫不掩藏其愤怒与挫败。</p>\n<p>\n\tSo why is it that for all the outrage and mourning with every mass shooting, nothing seems to change?究竟是为什么，每次大规模射杀事件后的愤怒与哀痛过后，似乎又一切如常、无所改变?</p>\n<p>\n\tTo understand that, it's important to grasp not just the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/stunning\" target=\"_blank\">stunning</a> statistics about gun ownership and gun violence in the United States, but America's very unique relationship with guns &mdash; unlike that of any other developed country.要明白这一切，不仅仅要抓牢触目惊心的美帝枪支控制和枪支暴力数据，更要懂得美国和枪支特别的关系，这和其它任何一个发达国家都有所不同。</p>\n<p>\n\t英语君挑选了以下7张大图告诉你如何看懂美国暴力和枪支：</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201606/e8f7510d-2e9e-4b4f-8327-e99c7b7f46ea_00.png\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t美帝枪支持有率趋势调查</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201606/e8f7510d-2e9e-4b4f-8327-e99c7b7f46ea_01.png\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t世界各国每100人中持枪者人数</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201606/e8f7510d-2e9e-4b4f-8327-e99c7b7f46ea_02.jpeg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t澳大利亚枪支回购项目启动后持火器自杀率</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201606/e8f7510d-2e9e-4b4f-8327-e99c7b7f46ea_03.jpeg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t持枪率与持枪伤亡率分析图</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201606/e8f7510d-2e9e-4b4f-8327-e99c7b7f46ea_04.jpeg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t每100万人中火器他杀率</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201606/e8f7510d-2e9e-4b4f-8327-e99c7b7f46ea_06.png\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201606/e8f7510d-2e9e-4b4f-8327-e99c7b7f46ea_08.png\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t持枪自由民意调查</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201606/e8f7510d-2e9e-4b4f-8327-e99c7b7f46ea_07.png\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t美国各州持枪和枪支伤亡分析图</p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #999999;\">\n\t声明：本双语文章的中文翻译系沪江英语原创内容，转载请注明出处。中文翻译仅代表译者个人观点，仅供参考。如有不妥之处，欢迎指正。</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p786121/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p786121\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p785541/\">不想四六级考懵逼？这里有你想要的~</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p784780/\">双语美文：你要成为自己的那道光</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p784456/\">能当英文名的花&花语：维多利亚时代就有！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p785836/\">欧洲杯：如何用英语和球迷愉快交谈</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p785858/\">奥兰多枪杀案凶手是gay？！曾在迪士尼踩点</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en